      <title>焦点：力拓因水污染指控与投资者发生争执</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/rio-tinto-wrangles-investors-over-water-contamination-claims-2024-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球矿业巨头力拓 (Rio Tinto) 在 2020 年摧毁了澳大利亚一处古老的原住民遗址后引发了公愤，现在面临着来自具有社会意识的投资者和贷款机构的新压力，这次是针对其两个矿山的用水做法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/rio-tinto-wrangles-investors-over-water-contamination-claims-2024-02-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 01:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
