      <title>独家：Engged Capital 获得 VF 继承人的支持，以撼动 North Face 所有者</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/engaged-capital-gains-support-vf-heirs-shake-up-north-face-owner-2024-02-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位继承人告诉路透社，维权投资者 Engaged Capital 得到了 VF Corp 创始家族的支持，致力于推动 North Face、Vans 和 Timberland 品牌所有者的董事会席位和更快的变革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/engaged-capital-gains-support-vf-heirs-shake-up-north-face-owner-2024-02-12/</guid>
